titleNullable: Extra Labels for RFCX competition data
subtitleNullable: Extra Labels for RFCX competition data
descriptionNullable:
### Context

This dataset consist of extra complementary true positive labels of the audio data listed in the Rainforest Connecttion Species Audio Detection Competition https://www.kaggle.com/c/rfcx-species-audio-detection/data . All data provided here are hand labelled

### Content

-  extra_labels_v1.csv : initial extra labels of train_tp.csv
-  extra_labels_v2.csv : additional extra labels on top of extra_labels_v1.csv and including extra_labels_v1.csv
-  extra_labels_v3.csv : additional extra labels on top of extra_labels_v2.csv and including extra_labels_v2.csv
-  extra_labels_v4.csv : additional extra labels on top of extra_labels_v3.csv and including extra_labels_v3.csv
- extra_labels_v5.csv : corrected what I thought was wrongly annotated for species 15 and replace with species 12
- extra_labels_v6.csv : removed some false species 15 true positives from  extra_labels_v4.csv
- extra_labels_v7.csv : additional extra labels on top of extra_labels_v6.csv and including extra_labels_v6.csv
- extra_labels_v8.csv : additional extra labels on top of extra_labels_v7.csv and including extra_labels_v7.csv
- extra_labels_v9.csv: remove false true positives from extra_labels_v8.csv based on train_fp.csv
- extra_labels_v71.csv : removed some rows from extra_labels_v7.csv and change column names
- extra_fp_label_v2.csv : extra true positive labels for train_fp.csv
- extra_fp_label_v3.csv :  additional extra labels on top of extra_fp_label_v2.csv and including extra_fp_label_v2.csv
- extra_fp_label_v4.csv :  additional extra labels on top of extra_fp_label_v3.csv and including extra_fp_label_v3.csv
- extra_fp_label_v5.csv :  additional extra labels on top of extra_fp_label_v4.csv and including extra_fp_label_v4.csv
- noisy_indexes_fp_tp_v5.csv : noisy or not noisy for the recording ids in extra_fp_label_v*.csv
- noisy_tp_rec_ids.csv: noisy or not noisy for the recording ids in train_tp.csv based on extra labels in extra_labels_v7.csv


### Acknowledgements

Credits to @meaninglesslives for creating extra_labels_v71.csv
